Opened the PR: [entireio/skills#17](https://github.com/entireio/skills/pull/17)

Added:
- YAML issue forms for bug reports, skill requests, and skill improvements
- A simple Markdown PR template

And yes, people can still open regular blank issues because we did not add a `config.yml` disabling them. PR templates are also advisory: contributors can edit or remove the prefilled text.

Validation:
- YAML loaded successfully for all issue forms
- `git diff --check -- .github`

